Introduction

Kim Jae Joong also known as Jaejoong and as J-Jun in Japan, is a South Korean Singer-songwriter, Actor, Director, and Designer under iNKODE. He is a member of the boy group JYJ and a former member of TVXQ!. He made his solo debut on January 17, 2013, with the mini album I.

On May 4th, 2023, Kim Jae Joong created his own company called, iNKODE.

On July 27th, 2023, he started a weekly YouTube show called Jaefriends, where he interviews various celebrities.
